item.title: CVE-2018-8312|2024-08-05T06:54:35.302Z -- microsoft -- microsoft%20access
item.description: A remote code execution vulnerability exists when Microsoft Access fails to properly handle objects in memory, aka "Microsoft Access Remote Code Execution Vulnerability." This affects Microsoft Access, Microsoft Office.
